PARAGRAPH BOUNDARY VERIFICATION (no changes needed)
================================================================================

compute_window_counts() already handles boundary ramp correctly:

  - Token at position 0: before_pos < 0 → break → 0-1-N (N = min(6, len-1))
  - Token at position 2: gets 2-1-N
  - Last token: after_pos >= length → break → N-1-0
  - Short paragraph (5 words): produces 0-1-4, 1-1-3, 2-1-2, 3-1-1, 4-1-0
  - Paragraph separator: re.split(r'\n\s*\n', text) → double newline = wall
  - Each paragraph windowed independently, counts merge safely

No patch needed. Behavior is already correct.


